en:
Find the bike you need to get around the holiday trail! We hope to provide you with the best facilities to discover and enjoy Normandy by bike. 
Our fleet consists of electrically assisted bikes, mountain bikes, VTC, junior bikes, road bikes, fitness bikes, tandem bikes, children's trailers.

Bike delivery and collection service, daily, weekend and weekly rentals.
